{"tid":1335931,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"王翰《涼州詞》","createTime":"2019-07-20T17:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T19:30:41.000Z","uid":15935,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa34b04b1a8ab9bc7dfd881b42232cd942aa454","tid":1335931,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"葡萄美酒夜光杯，欲飲琵琶馬上催。醉臥沙場君莫笑，古來征戰幾人回。<br />\n<br />\n估唔到今晚都會有呢種即將上戰場嘅悲壯感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />昔日東方之珠竟然就嚟落得亡國嘅下場，絕對唔可以！<br />\n各位落到場要互相照應，痛痛快快為我地嘅香港打場勝仗，保家衛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568904ff871f1d89581c9391c03d928cdf26f9b8","tid":1335931,"uid":37156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:30:41.000Z","msg":"夏蕙姨! 點算?"}]}